\c 29
\s Incwadi kaJeremiya kwabathunjelwe eBhabhiloni
\p
\v 1 La-ke ngamazwi encwadi ayithumelayo uJeremiya umprofethi ivela eJerusalema isiya kunsali yabadala babathunjiweyo\x + 19.1. Hez. 8.1.\x* lakubapristi\x + 23.33.\x* lakubaprofethi lebantwini bonke ayebathumbile uNebhukadinezari besuka eJerusalema wabasa eBhabhiloni
\v 2 (emva kokuphuma kukaJekoniya inkosi,\x + 2 Kho. 24.12,15.\x*\x + 24.1.\x* lendlovukazi,\x + 2 Kho. 24.12,15.\x*\x + 22.26.\x* labathenwa,\x + 2 Kho. 24.12,15.\x* iziphathamandla zakoJuda lezeJerusalema,\x + 24.1.\x* lababazi,\x + 24.1.\x* labakhandi,\x + 24.1.\x* besuka eJerusalema),
\v 3 ngesandla sikaElasa indodana kaShafani,\x + 2 Lan. 34.8.\x* loGemariya indodana kaHilikhiya,\x + 1 Lan. 6.13.\x* uZedekhiya inkosi yakoJuda eyabathuma eBhabhiloni kuNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 51.59.\x* isithi:
\v 4 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, kibo bonke abathunjiweyo engabenza bathunjwa besuswa eJerusalema basiwa eBhabhiloni:
\v 5 Yakhani izindlu,\x + 28 .28. Hez. 11.3.\x* lihlale \add kizo\add*, lihlanyele izivande, lidle izithelo zazo;
\v 6 lithathe abafazi, lizale amadodana lamadodakazi, lithathele amadodana enu abafazi, lendise amadodakazi enu emadodeni, ukuze azale amadodana lamadodakazi, lande khona, linganciphi.
\v 7 Lidinge ukuthula komuzi lapho engilithumbele khona, liwukhulekele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni;\x + Ezra 6.10. 1 Tim. 2.2.\x* ngoba ekuthuleni kwawo lizakuba lokuthula.
\p
\v 8 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Akuthi abaprofethi benu labavumisi benu\x + 27.9.\x* abaphakathi kwenu bangalikhohlisi;\x + Mat. 24.4.\x* lingawalaleli amaphupho enu eliwenza aphutshwe;\x + 27.9.\x*
\v 9 ngoba baprofetha amanga kini ngebizo lami;\x + 14.14; 28 .21,23,31.\x* kangibathumanga,\x + 14.14; 29 .21,23.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 10 Ngoba itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Qiniso, lapho iminyaka engamatshumi ayisikhombisa isigcwalisekile eBhabhiloni,\x + 25.12.\x* ngizalihambela,\x + 27.22.\x* ngiqinise ilizwi lami elihle kini,\x + 24.6; 33.14.\x* ukuthi ngilibuyise kulindawo.\x + 27.22.\x*\x + 24.6; 33.14.\x*
\v 11 Ngoba mina ngiyazi imicabango engiyicabanga ngani, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, imicabango yokuthula, kayisiyo eyokubi, ukuthi ngilinike isiphetho lokulindelweyo.\x + 31.17. 1 Kor. 10.13.\x*
\v 12 Khona lizangibiza\x + 33.3. Dan. 9.3.\x* liyekhuleka kimi, ngilizwe.
\v 13 Njalo lizangidinga,\x + 33.3. Dan. 9.3.\x*\x + 2 Lan. 15.2. Hos. 3.5. Levi 26.39,40. Dute. 30.1.\x*\x + 10.18. Dute. 4.29. Hlab. 32.6; 78.34. Isa. 55.6.\x* li\add ngi\add*thole, lapho lingidingisisa ngenhliziyo yenu yonke.\x + 24.7.\x*
\v 14 Njalo ngizatholwa yini,\x + 10.18. Dute. 4.29. Hlab. 32.6; 78.34. Isa. 55.6.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngibuyise ukuthunjwa kwenu,\x + 30.3.\x* ngiliqoqe kuzo zonke izizwe\x + 23.3; 32.37. Hlab. 107.3.\x* lakuzo zonke indawo lapho engilixotshele khona,\x + 8.3; 29.18.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngilibuyise endaweni engalithumba livela khona.
\p
\v 15 Ngoba litshilo: IN\nd kosi\nd* isivusele abaprofethi eBhabhiloni.
\v 16 Ngoba utsho njalo uJehova ngenkosi ehlezi esihlalweni sobukhosi sikaDavida\x + 22.2.\x* langabo bonke abantu abahlala kulumuzi, abafowenu abangaphumelanga ekuthunjweni kanye lani:
\v 17 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla: Khangelani, ngizathumela phakathi kwabo inkemba, indlala, lomatshayabhuqe wesifo,\x + 24.10.\x* ngibenze babe njengemikhiwa eyenyanyekayo, engadlekiyo ngenxa yobubi.\x + 24.8.\x*
\v 18 Ngixotshane labo ngenkemba, ngendlala, langomatshayabhuqe wesifo, ngibanikele ukuba yisesabiso kuyo yonke imibuso yomhlaba,\x + 24.9. Dute. 28.25.\x* babe yisiqalekiso,\x + 42.18.\x*\x + 23.10. Dute. 29.19. Dan. 9.11. Zek. 5.3.\x* lento eyesabekayo,\x + 42.18.\x*\x + 2 Kho. 22.19.\x*\x + 2 Lan. 29.8.\x* lokuncifelwayo,\x + 2 Lan. 29.8.\x* lehlazo,\x + 42.18.\x* phakathi kwazo zonke izizwe\x + 26.6.\x* lapho engibaxotshele khona;\x + 29 .18.\x*
\v 19 ngenxa yokuthi bengawalalelanga amazwi ami, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, engawathumela kibo ngenceku zami abaprofethi, ngivuka ngovivi ngi\add ba\add*thuma,\x + 2 Lan. 36.15.\x* kodwa kalilalelanga,\x + 25.3\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 20 Lina-ke zwanini ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, lina lonke bathunjiweyo, engabathuma besuka eJerusalema besiya eBhabhiloni:\x + 24.5.\x*
\v 21 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, mayelana loAhabi indodana kaKolaya, lamayelana loZedekhiya indodana kaMahaseya, abaprofetha amanga kini ngebizo lami:\x + 29 .9\x* Khangelani, ngizabanikela esandleni sikaNebhukadirezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni, ozababulala phambi kwamehlo enu.
\v 22 Njalo kuzathathwa kubo\x + Isa. 65.15.\x* isiqalekiso yibo bonke abathunjiweyo koJuda abaseBhabhiloni\x + 24.9.\x* kuthiwe: Kungathi iN\nd kosi\nd* ikumise njengoZedekhiya lanjengoAhabi, inkosi yeBhabhiloni eyamosa ngomlilo;\x + Dan. 3.6.\x*
\v 23 ngenxa yokuthi benze ubuthutha koIsrayeli, bafeba labafazi babomakhelwane babo,\x + 23.14.\x* baqamba amazwi angamanga ngebizo lami,\x + 29 .9.\x*\x + 23.14.\x* engingabalayanga wona; njalo yimi engaziyo, e\add ngi\add*ngumfakazi,\x + Mal. 3.5.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 24 Uzakhuluma kuShemaya umNehelami usithi:
\v 25 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, isithi: Ngenxa yokuthi wena uthumele izincwadi ngebizo lakho kubo bonke abantu abaseJerusalema, lakuZefaniya\x + 2 Kho. 25.18.\x* indodana kaMahaseya umpristi,\x + 35.4.\x* lakubo bonke abapristi, usithi:
\v 26 IN\nd kosi\nd* isikwenze ube ngumpristi esikhundleni sikaJehoyada umpristi,\x + 2 Kho. 11.15. 2 Lan. 23.16.\x* ukuthi libe ngababonisi bendlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 20.1.\x* phezu kwakhe wonke umuntu ohlanyayo\x + 2 Kho. 9.11.\x* ozitshaya umprofethi,\x + 1 Sam. 18.10. 1 Kho. 18.29.\x* ukuthi limfake esitokisini elezankosi entanyeni.\x + 20.2.\x*
\v 27 Khathesi-ke, kungani ungamkhuzanga uJeremiya umAnathothi\x + 1.1.\x* ozitshaya umprofethi kini?\x + 1 Sam. 18.10. 1 Kho. 18.29.\x*
\v 28 Ngoba ngenxa yalokhu usethumele kithi \add e\add*Bhabhiloni esithi: Kuzakuba kude; yakhani izindlu,\x + 29 .5.\x* lihlale \add kizo\add*, lihlanyele izivande, lidle izithelo zazo.
\v 29 UZefaniya umpristi waseyifunda lincwadi endlebeni zikaJeremiya umprofethi.
\p
\v 30 Laselifika ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* kuJeremiya lisithi:
\v 31 Thumela kubo bonke abathunjiweyo usithi: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* ngoShemaya umNehelami: Ngenxa yokuthi uShemaya eprofethe kini, mina-ke ngingamthumanga,\x + 28.15.\x*\x + 29 .9.\x* walenza ukuthi lithembe amanga,\x + 28.15.\x*
\v 32 ngakho itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*: Khangela, ngizajezisa uShemaya umNehelami kanye lenzalo yakhe; kayikuba lamuntu ozahlala phakathi kwalababantu, angaboni okuhle engizakwenzela abantu bami,\x + 17.6.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngoba ukhulume ukuhlamuka emelene leN\nd kosi\nd*.\x + 28.16.\x*